column2: SELECT TOP #   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,p.extinction_u,p.extinction_r,p.extinction_g,p.extinction_i,p.extinction_z,   p.dered_u,p.dered_r,p.dered_g,p.dered_i,p.dered_z,s.class,s.z as redshift FROM PhotoObj AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE     redshift BETWEEN # AND #    AND s.class=GALAXY&&&
